no way to live.

09:38.870 --> 09:39.904
Pshaw!

09:39.938 --> 09:41.172
Pshaw, I say!

09:41.206 --> 09:42.706
Pshaw yourself!

09:42.741 --> 09:44.475
Pshaw!
Pshaw!

09:44.509 --> 09:45.810
Homer, do something!

09:45.844 --> 09:47.611
They're killing each other!

09:47.646 --> 09:49.580
Oh, yeah?

09:49.614 --> 09:52.399
The world may have despised
Glamorous Godfrey,

09:52.434 --> 09:54.702
but that conceited
mother-puncher was my hero.

09:56.304 --> 09:58.339
Please, Abe, let
me buy you dinner

09:58.373 --> 10:00.674
in exchange for a few
tales of the golden age

10:00.709 --> 10:02.076
of professional
grappling.

10:02.110 --> 10:06.797
Sorry, I been trying to forget
those days for 50 years.

10:06.832 --> 10:08.165
But, Grampa,

10:08.200 --> 10:10.100
I want to hear about
old-time wrestling, too.

10:10.135 --> 10:12.486
Well, it looks like
you've made a new fan.

10:12.521 --> 10:15.322
It'd be a shame to
let him down, hmm?

10:15.357 --> 10:16.323
Fine.

10:16.358 --> 10:17.791
One dinner.

10:17.826 --> 10:19.093
Excellent.

10:19.127 --> 10:21.278
So we'll take the boy
and make a night of it.

10:21.313 --> 10:22.379
I don't know.

10:22.414 --> 10:24.047
Should I really
let the men

10:24.065 --> 10:25.916
who ruined my
past and present

10:25.951 --> 10:28.469
