going to ruin my future?

10:28.503 --> 10:29.637
I'll bring you home
my dessert.

10:29.671 --> 10:31.138
Text me the choices.

10:31.172 --> 10:32.840
<i>I can't believe I'm on the town</i>

10:32.874 --> 10:35.776
with Glamorous Godfrey
himself.

10:35.810 --> 10:39.163
Tell me of your epic battle
with Swedish Olaf Johannsen.

10:39.197 --> 10:42.917
Oh, yeah,
"The Fury of the Fjords."

10:50.458 --> 10:52.509
You settled
that Swede's meatballs.

10:52.544 --> 10:54.995
What I wouldn't give
to see Glamorous Godfrey

10:55.030 --> 10:56.530
in action once more.

10:56.565 --> 10:58.032
Would you ever consider

10:58.066 --> 10:59.900
throwing your wig
back into the ring?

10:59.935 --> 11:01.969
Go back to
being a villain?

11:02.003 --> 11:03.370
Oh, forget that.

11:03.405 --> 11:06.173
Being hated is the
worst feeling there is.

11:07.275 --> 11:08.909
You've got it all wrong,
my friend.

11:08.944 --> 11:10.477
Once you see it my way,

11:10.512 --> 11:12.813
you'll understand
that being hated

11:12.847 --> 11:15.316
is the greatest
feeling in the world.

