12:59.606 --> 13:01.474
but he's really
a straight-up psycho.

13:01.508 --> 13:04.260
Your grandfather
is not psycho.

13:04.294 --> 13:07.463
The only thing he's
"straight-up" is loves you.

13:07.497 --> 13:10.199
Gorilla Joe, Gorilla Sam,
Gorilla Pete,

13:10.233 --> 13:12.368
Ook and Eek, the Gorilla Twins.

13:12.402 --> 13:15.204
Where did Mr. Burns dig up
all these old wrestlers?

13:15.238 --> 13:16.605
Apparently, old folks homes

13:16.640 --> 13:19.075
are full of people
that used to be things.

13:19.109 --> 13:21.594
Just like you and me.
Swear to God.

13:21.628 --> 13:24.096
Welcome, aficionados
of the roped ring,

13:24.131 --> 13:26.749
to a thrilling night
of senior-on-senior action.

13:36.860 --> 13:38.844
Folding chairs!
Folding chairs!

13:38.879 --> 13:40.780
Can't hit somebody when
they're not looking

13:40.814 --> 13:42.248
without a
folding chair!

13:42.282 --> 13:43.249
Can I have one?

13:43.283 --> 13:44.300
Can I?
Fine.

13:44.334 --> 13:45.601
Ha!

13:45.635 --> 13:47.620
And now our main event.

13:47.654 --> 13:50.539
In this corner,
Baby Face Palooka.

13:50.574 --> 13:51.807
And entering the ring,

13:51.842 --> 13:54.577
America's original
vainglorious bastard,

13:54.611 --> 13:56.278
Glamorous Godfrey!

14:05.288 --> 14:07.273
Yes,
feel the hatred.

14:07.307 --> 14:10.943
It makes you strong,
powerful, alive.

14:10.977 --> 14:14.380
You are the luckiest people
in the world!

14:14.414 --> 14:16.382
You get to look at me!

14:22.239 --> 14:23.439
